# Chinese Poetry API - manual test requests
# Compatible with the VS Code "REST Client" extension and JetBrains HTTP Client.
# Server must be running (`make run-server` or `./build/server`), default port 1279.

@host = http://localhost:1279
@authorId = 1
@dynastyId = 6
@typeId = 11


### Health check
GET {{host}}/api/v1/health


### Overall statistics
GET {{host}}/api/v1/stats


# Poems

### List poems (paginated, simplified Chinese default)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems?page=1&page_size=20

### List poems, traditional Chinese
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems?lang=zh-Hant&page=1&page_size=10

### Random poem
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/random

### Random poem filtered by author
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/random?author=李白

### Random poem filtered by type + dynasty
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/random?type=五言绝句&dynasty=唐

### Random poem filtered by multiple types (OR)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/random?author=李白&dynasty=唐&type=五言绝句&type=七言绝句&type=五言律诗

### Random poem filtered by IDs
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/random?author_id={{authorId}}&dynasty_id={{dynastyId}}&type_id={{typeId}}


# Search (FTS5-backed, see internal/database/migrate.go)

### Search all fields (title + content + author) - common phrase
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/search?q=静夜思

### Search all fields - single/double CJK character (trigram tokenizer handles short queries)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/search?q=月

### Search title only
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/search?q=庐山&type=title

### Search content only
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/search?q=明月光&type=content

### Search author only
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/search?q=李白&type=author

### Search with pagination
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/search?q=月&page=2&page_size=10

### Search with no matches (sanity check for empty result handling)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/poems/search?q=不存在的内容不存在


# Authors

### List authors
GET {{host}}/api/v1/authors?page=1&page_size=20

### Get a single author by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/authors/{{authorId}}


# Dynasties

### List dynasties (with poem/author counts)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/dynasties

### Get a single dynasty by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/dynasties/{{dynastyId}}


# Poetry types

### List poetry types
GET {{host}}/api/v1/types

### Get a single poetry type by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/types/{{typeId}}


# GraphQL

### Search poems (GraphQL equivalent of the FTS search above)
POST {{host}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query($q: String!) { searchPoems(query: $q, searchType: ALL, page: 1, pageSize: 10) { totalCount edges { node { id title author { name } dynasty { name } } } } }",
  "variables": { "q": "静夜思" }
}

### Get a single poem by ID
POST {{host}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query($id: ID!) { poem(id: $id) { id title content author { name } dynasty { name } type { name } } }",
  "variables": { "id": "1" }
}

### List poems with filters
POST {{host}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { poems(page: 1, pageSize: 10, dynastyId: 6) { totalCount pageInfo { hasNextPage } edges { node { id title } } } }"
}

### Random poem (GraphQL)
POST {{host}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { randomPoem { id title author { name } } }"
}

### Statistics
POST {{host}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { statistics { totalPoems totalAuthors totalDynasties poemsByDynasty { dynasty { name } count } } }"
}
